</P>
<P>
   One theory was that the rebel effort will now disintegrate and
factions of the RUF will switch allegiance to the government.
Others fear a new commander could emerge, and that the savage,
anarchic struggle will continue.
</P>
<P>
   ``Relations between Sankoh and his troops are complex,'' one
diplomat said, acknowledging the fluidity of the situation.
</P>
<P>
   Before Sankoh was taken into custody _ possibly betrayed by some
