<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-19 13:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9844 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-NONCOMPETE-ART-BOS &LR;      05-19 1510
