<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-19 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9869 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-JACKSON-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      05-19 0782
