<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: A CORRECTED VERSION OF THE HEMMINGS FEATURE IS BEING MOVED
TO THE WIRE. 
THE NEW VERSION CORRECTS THE WRITER'S NAME FROM GLENN WHIPP TO REED
JOHNSON. 
 

</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 

<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
