Rudolph Giuliani from the U.S. Senate race in New York opens the
door for Rep. Rick Lazio, a moderate Republican from Long Island,
to enter the race against First Lady Hillary Rodham Clinton. We
look at what Giuliani can do with the millions of dollars he has
raised for the campaign. By DAN FREEDMAN and STEWART M. POWELL.
