<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MEXICO-FOX-$ADV21-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POPULIST FORMER COKE EXECUTIVE CLOSING IN ON MEXICO'S RULING
PARTY
 &HT;    With Photos.
