America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    AGAINST ALL ODDS. With all the hype, it's getting very hard to
distinguish what is real and what is virtual in the increasingly
insane web world. In an exclusive interview, Lycos CEO Robert Davis
talks to LATIN TRADE editor Mike Zellner about what's hot and
what's not in digital Latin America.
