<P>
   BRAZIL-SUGAR (Sertaozinho, Brazil) _ Winds of change are blowing
through Brazil's creaking cane sugar industry, by far its biggest
and in many ways its most backward. By Simon Romero.
</P>
<P>
   With Graphic.
</P>
<P>
   MARKET-WATCH (Undated) _ The Market Watch column: Some experts
believe that volatility is a function of stock price gains. But
Federal Reserve chairman Alan Greenspan believes it may be a
consequence of the waves of new information buffeting the market.
By Alex Berenson.
