<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-19 20:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0388 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-EURO-TOURISM-ART-1070     05-19 1139
