<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-19 21:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0579 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f BC-BIZBUDGET-FINANCE-SFC     05-19 0226
